'''Squarn's Junkyard''' was located on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Muugrah]], close to the city of [[Slaibo]], and was owned by the junk dealer [[Squarn]]. Sometime during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], a group of [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebels]] looking for spare parts to repair their [[Hyperdrive/Legends|hyperdrive]] landed here and were met by [[Klev (assistant)|Klev]] who introduced them to Squarn. They hired a [[Repulsorlift/Legends|repulsorlift]] [[Skiff/Legends|skiff]] and set about exploring the junkyard to find the pieces they needed. During this search they came across the [[Astromech droid/Legends|astromech]] [[Droid/Legends|droid]] [[R2-D6]] in a battle damaged Rebel [[BTL Y-wing starfighter/Legends|Y-wing]]. Once they had freed him and bought him from Squarn they continued their search but were eventually attacked by a group of [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]] also looking for Deesix. They managed to defeat this group thanks to the help of Squarn's [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] and soon left to deliver Deesix to a Rebel base.

